The paper deals with automated disease classification within dermoscopic images using deep learning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of transfer learning and preprocessing techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the evaluation of the proposed solution on a specific dataset indicates a potential interest in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
